Websockets
==========

Currently in Beta.

| Network   | Description        | URL                                                                                  |
|-----------|--------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Mainnet   | production network | [wss://mainnet.infura.io/ws](wss://mainnet.infura.io/ws)     |
| Ropsten   | test network       | [wss://ropsten.infura.io/ws](wss://ropsten.infura.io/ws)     |
| Rinkeby   | test network       | [wss://rinkeby.infura.io/ws](wss://rinkeby.infura.io/ws)     |

During the Beta, authentication is not required.  However, authentication will be required as part of the general availability release later this year.
